(128, 'Mononoke', 'Mononoke', 'https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/3/20713.jpg', 'TV', 12, 'Jul 13, 2007 to Sep 28, 2007', '22 min. per ep.', 'R - 17+ (violence & profanity)', 8.46, 36972, 129, 664, 'The main protagonist of the series, Kusuriuri, was first introduced in \"Bakeneko,\" the final chapter of the Ayakashi: Japanese Classic Horror anthology series. Mononoke was originally broadcast during the NoitaminA programming block in Japan.', 'Toei Animation', 'Mystery, Historical, Horror, Demons, Psychological, Supernatural, Fantasy, Seinen'),
