(255, 'Initial D First Stage', 'Initial D First Stage', 'https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/13/6801.jpg', 'TV', 26, 'Apr 19, 1998 to Dec 6, 1998', '25 min. per ep.', 'PG-13 - Teens 13 or older', 8.28, 60560, 256, 745, 'A sizable number of racing games based on the franchise were released for arcades, home consoles, handhelds and PC. Japan\'s Avex Inc. and Hong Kong\'s Media Asia Group co-produced a live-action film based on Initial D. It was released on Jun 23, 2005 across Asia. While the film deviated considerably from the original story, it was nominated for multiple awards and won many of them, at the Hong Kong Film Awards and Golden Horse Awards.', 'Studio Gallop, Studio Comet', 'Action, Cars, Drama, Seinen, Sports'),
